{"tid":1921941,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"認為情況不到 1987、2008 年那麼嚴重，巴菲特：待得夠久就會看盡一切市場變化","createTime":"2020-03-12T09:15:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T11:03:27.000Z","uid":298405,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ba51274c13176161328f843d93b33ff640069b80","tid":1921941,"uid":298405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:15:19.000Z","msg":"由於<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">武漢肺炎</span></span>疫情與油價下跌，歐美股市近期經歷劇烈震盪，當被問到對股災的看法時，波克夏海瑟威執行長巴菲特（Warren Buffett）雖然承認這確實是兩下重擊，但也強調，目前事情並沒有 1987 年或 2008 年金融危機嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n隨著武漢肺炎疫情在歐美蔓延，道瓊工業平均指數 9 日迎接 2008 年金融危機以來最大單日跌幅，這也是史上首次下跌超過 2,000 點，包含蘋果、高盛、波音都下挫，這讓許多人開始擔心更嚴重的經濟衰退是否來臨。<br />\n<br />\n但巴菲特似乎不這麼想。3 日他甚至還搶購更多達美航空股票，似乎相當有信心受重創的航空業將會復甦。<br />\n<br />\n近日受訪時，巴菲特表示，武漢肺炎疫情和油價波動確實為美股帶來兩下重擊，但截至目前，情況還無法與 1987 年黑色星期一相提並論，只是算「仿製品」，2008 年金融海嘯發生的事都比現在可怕多了。<br />\n<br />\n在巴菲特看來，如果在股市待得夠久，就會看過一切。「這也許花了我 89 年將這經驗付諸實踐，投資者如果分分秒秒都盯著市場，自然對新聞的反應就會很大。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.technews.tw/2020/03/12/warren-buffett-dont-think-coronavirus-will-hit-stocks-so-bad/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.technews.tw%2F2020%2F03%2F12%2Fwarren-buffett-dont-think-coronavirus-will-hit-stocks-so-bad%2F&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9leaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=2f7f3444\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.technews.tw/2020/03/12/warren-buffett-dont-think-coronavirus-will-hit-stocks-so-bad/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foxbusiness.com/markets/warren-buffett-says-coronavirus-oil-price-war-one-two-punch-not-as-bad-as-1987-2008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxbusiness.com%2Fmarkets%2Fwarren-buffett-says-coronavirus-oil-price-war-one-two-punch-not-as-bad-as-1987-2008&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9leaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=d64d457c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxbusiness.com/markets/warren-buffett-says-coronavirus-oil-price-war-one-two-punch-not-as-bad-as-1987-2008</a>"},{"pid":"d04a519913dda3e6540e3acb8c27d1e4c33ec200","tid":1921941,"uid":125888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:13:05.000Z","msg":"89歲(破產)"},{"pid":"5644c1061a33919ff9c0c33f949b7a654061293b","tid":1921941,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:31:39.000Z","msg":"講野仲玄過嗇色園高僧"},{"pid":"f97b82290d45e239cf62d3e1d4c7821803f33ea0","tid":1921941,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:36:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a1f3e85bc2577dc5f36477cc17723c9876d1cdf","tid":1921941,"uid":169071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:44:38.000Z","msg":"佛系投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f44acec664b120d49b2f6f77a63a100111903ce","tid":1921941,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:03:27.000Z","msg":"etorro"}]}